[http://open-labware.net/ Open-Labware.net] is a spin-off project of [http://trendinafrica.org/ TReND in Africa] and the [http://badenlab.org/ Baden lab]. Presents designs and modifications of [[Free and Open Source Hardware]] projects specifically intended to be used in a scientific lab or research setting. See also the [[Open-source lab]]

==Projects==
* [http://open-labware.net/projects/flypi/ FlyPi] - A 3-D printable open source platform for fluorescence microscopy, optogenetics and accurate temperature control.
* [http://open-labware.net/projects/biropettes/ Biropettes] - 3-D printable micropipette
* [http://open-labware.net/projects/micromanipulator/ Motorized micromanipulator]
* [http://open-labware.net/projects/phone-scope/ phonescope]

